<br>
<br>
Can you Dazzle us with your story of a might battle?<br>
Can you Charm us with your tales of virtue?<br>
Can you Humble us with your songs of glory?<br>
Can you Confound us with you spells of wisdom?<br>
<br>
The Ring of Mystic Souls proudly announces the Storyteller Contest! We are calling all Poets, Comedians, Trubadours, Storytellers and Performers to show their skills on the stage in Freeport!<br>
<br>
If you can win the hearts of the jury you will receive the title of the Greatest Storyteller and a purse containing no less than 1000 platinum coins! <br>
<br>
(OOC)<br>
<br>
Just the facts:<br>
<br>
1. The Ring of Mystic Souls will hold the Storyteller Contest on Sunday, April 27th, 22.00 UK time (that's 23.00 Euro, 17.00 Eastern US and 14.00 Western US).<br>
<br>
2. To enter the contest, please apply below. Seven contestants will be chosen by the Mystic Souls from those interested, based on their how artistic/entertaining are their applications. <br>
<br>
3. The contest itself will be judged by a 5 person jury, one Mystic Soul and four representatives from other guilds. In case one of the invited jurors is unable to attend, a Mystic Soul will step in to replace him.<br>
<br>
4. Every one of the contestants will have the stage for 3 minutes. Once all the 7 entrants perform, the jury will choose two finalists. They will make another appearance, once again 3 minutes. After that the jury will make the final decision.<br>
<br>
5. The winner will be awarded 1000pp, the runner up will receive 200pp. All entrants will receive minor prizes.<br>
<br>
6. There will be other accompanying events, including a ballot, free drinks and snacks.<br>
<br>
If you want to learn more, please contact <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Skafid</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> when adventuring in Norrath.<br>
