<br>
Swirling the edge of her midnight blue skirts as she read the note, Lethe was greeted by her daughter Suliene.  &quot;Mother, you would do well in this contest.  You should enter.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Perhaps I shall, my dear,&quot; Lethe responded to her youngest child.<br>
<br>
Pulling a pen and her special ink from one of her satchels, Lethe added her information to the listing:<br>
<br>
Lethe Wren<br>
Teir'dal Enchantress of the 52nd ranking<br>
Guild Leader of Destiny's Path<br>
<br>
Blowing a bit of her lavendar scented powder across the ink to help it dry, Lethe looked over her penmanship to make certain it was all appropriately done.  She smiled to herself and followed her daughter off on their way back to their home. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"> <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.gothictiger.net/images/lethesig" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.freeopendiary.com/entrylist.asp?authorcode=A846251">History</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> | <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.guildportal.com/Guild.aspx?GuildID=4352&amp;TabID=32364">Destiny's Path</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> | <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=441995">My Closet</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=melediweaver>melediweaver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dirges, a specialty</span><br>  Posts: 266<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/19/03 10:59:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=374.topic&index=12>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Story Telling Contest!!!</span><hr size=1> *ooks at the notice and sighs wistfully<br>
