<br>
&quot;The Storytellers willing to enter the contest are:<br>
<br>
Mudfish,  from the forbidden city of Cabilis<br>
Oenghus,  from the frozen Halas<br>
Raseac, a servant of the Tribunal<br>
Lethe, from the shadows of Neriak  &quot;<br>
<br>
Here Skafid pauses a bit and then adds:<br>
<br>
&quot;and perhaps <br>
<br>
Silenae, the mysterious one<br>
Laennie, the naturewalker&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
Who else will take the challange?<br>
<br>
<br>
(ooc)<br>
<br>
If you hesitate, whether you should enter - please, do try. It's all about fun and role-playing spirit. <br>
